### Attributes

Attribute          | Type    | Description
-------------------|---------|------------
created-at         | date    |
cover-letter       | string  |
changed-stage-at   | date    | Date when candidate was added to current stage
updated-at         | date    |
rejected-at        | date    | If set, the candidate has been rejected for this job
referring-url      | string  |
referring-site     | string  | __Read only__, friendly name parsed from referring-url (i.e. Facebook, Indeed etc)
sourced            | boolean |
send-default-reply | boolean | __Create only__, set to true if you want to send the "Default reply" email to the candidate. Default: false
send-user-notifications | boolean | __Create only__, set to true if you want to send notifications to users. Default: false

### Relations

The <code>job-application</code> object always has a relation to a <code>candidate</code> and a <code>job</code>

Relation  | Description
----------|------------
candidate |
job       |
stage     | Current stage (i.e Inbox, Reviewing, Hired)
